    "rich_text_YBPEqU": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_YgUn4M": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "MUMU BATH WHERE HERITAGE MEETS LUXURY"
          }
        },
        "richtext_xczdeX": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Handcrafted Asian-Inspired <strong>Bath<br/>Soaps </strong>by Mumu Bath</h2><p>Indulge in handcrafted soaps made<br/>with gentle, skin-loving botanicals. Each bar is thoughtfully designed to nourish, cleanse, and elevate your daily ritual.</p><p>Whether you're winding down or tarting fresh, our <strong>bathing soap</strong> collection offers<br/>the perfect blend of purity and purpose. No harsh chemicals - just beautiful, intentional skincare.</p><h2>Features That Make a Difference</h2><ul><li><strong>Plant-Based & Ultra-Mild </strong>– Our <strong>bathing soap </strong>is crafted with gentle botanicals. It soothes sensitive skin without causing dryness or irritation.<br/></li><li><strong>Deep Moisture, Zero Residue </strong>– Made with organic olive and coconut oils. It hydrates deeply while keeping pores clear.<br/></li><li><strong>Handcrafted Bath Staples </strong>\t– Our <strong>bath soaps </strong>are made in small batches. This ensures freshness, purity, and exceptional care in every bar.<br/></li><li><strong>Scented with Purpose  </strong>– Infused with rosemary and lavender essential oils. Each bar\tcalms your skin and uplifts your senses.<br/></li><li><strong>Barrier-Boosting Ingredients </strong>\t– Contains organic dill to relieve irritation. It helps restore and strengthen the skin's natural barrier.</li></ul><h2>Benefits of Using Our Soaps</h2><ul><li><strong>Naturally Nourishing  </strong>– Crafted with plant-based oils that hydrate without stripping your skin, perfect for daily use on sensitive skin.<br/></li><li><strong>Inspired by Heritage </strong>\t– Rooted in traditional <strong>Asian soap</strong> rituals, each \tbar blends cultural care with modern simplicity.<br/></li><li><strong>No Harsh Chemicals </strong>– Free from sulfates, parabens, and synthetic fragrances to keep your skin balanced and irritation-free.<br/></li><li><strong>Eco-Friendly Choice  </strong>– Plastic-free and biodegradable, making your skincare routine kind to the planet.<br/></li><li><strong>Trusted Ingredients </strong>– Our <strong>organic soap bars</strong> are made with high-quality botanicals and time-tested methods for clean, conscious skincare.<br/></li><li><strong>Artisan-Made in Small Batches </strong>\t– Handcrafted with intention to ensure premium quality and a noticeable difference in every wash.</li></ul><h2>How to Use Our Soaps</h2><ul><li><strong>Lather & Cleanse </strong>\t– Wet the bar and work into a rich lather. Massage gently onto damp skin, then rinse thoroughly for a fresh, clean feel.<br/></li><li><strong>Hydrate & Nourish </strong>– After cleansing, use our Lightweight Body Butter. It seals in moisture and complements the benefits of our <strong>organic soap</strong>. <br/></li><li><strong>Target Trouble Spots </strong>\t– Apply our Wonder Balm to dry or irritated areas. It works well after using soothing bars like our <strong>Asian soap</strong> blends.<br/></li><li><strong>Store with Care </strong>– Keep your soap on a well-draining dish. This prevents melting and extends the life of your bar.<br/></li><li><strong>Use Daily </strong>– Gentle enough for everyday use. Enjoy soft, balanced skin with\teach wash.</li></ul><h2>Why Shop From Us</h2><ul><li><strong>Rooted in Tradition </strong>– Inspired by time-honored rituals, our <strong>Asian \tsoap</strong> formulas combine cultural wisdom with modern purity. Each bar is a reflection of gentle, holistic care.<br/></li><li><strong>Sustainable & Ethical </strong>\t– We focus on eco-friendly practices from packaging to production. It’s skincare that feels good and does good.<br/></li><li><strong>Truly Clean Ingredients </strong>– We use only safe, natural, and skin-loving elements. Our <strong>organic \tsoap bars</strong> are free from synthetic additives and harsh chemicals.<br/></li><li><strong>Loved by Sensitive Skin </strong>– Our soaps are ultra-gentle, and dermatologist trusted. Customers with dry, reactive, or eczema-prone skin come back for a reason.</li></ul><h2>Your Daily Ritual, Elevated</h2><p>Each bar is made to bring comfort, calm, and care to your everyday routine. From soothing scents to skin-loving ingredients, our soaps are crafted with purpose. Free from harsh chemicals and full of nourishing botanicals, they support healthier, happier skin. Thoughtful formulas inspired by tradition and nature. Feel the difference from the first wash. Add a touch of intention to your self-care today.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
